    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Introducing WALKER GOLF THINGS",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Three years ago, four friends from across the globe set out to make something different. What began as plans for a skate brand shifted into something bigger—something rooted in golf, but infused with the energy of surf, skate, and street culture.</p><p>Walker Golf launched out of Australia's Gold Coast, founded on one simple idea: golf clothes that look good, feel good, and work wherever your day takes you. From the course, to the skatepark, to the pub, this is performance gear without the performance complex.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["heading_1", "text_1"],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
    "testim_1": {
      "type": "testimonial",
      "settings": {
        "testimonial_text": "<p>\"We were always kind of playing golf, talking golf, but also working in and around the skate industry,\" says co-founder Jack. \"It just felt like the right time to do something in this space, with our background.\"</p>",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "max_width": 1440,
        "margin_bottom": "medium"
      }
    },
    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>And what a background it is. With deep experience at brands like Adidas, Volcom, and Nike, the Walker crew didn't come to play small. What they've built is a brand that blends technical function with relaxed Australian cool - always clean, never boring.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["text_1"],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
    "media_grid_1": {
      "type": "media-grid",
      "blocks": {
        "image_1": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_adf4ba15-f865-4532-91d5-55b45424721b.png"
          }
        },
        "image_2": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_f63b1e45-7814-4708-bc54-7d82881c9c9d.png"
          }
        },
        "image_3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_241ddefb-56e7-44af-a508-18a0b3264f60.png"
          }
        },
        "image_4": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_f63b1e45-7814-4708-bc54-7d82881c9c9d.png"
